* VibroSense Block 03 — 4-Bit Binary-Weighted Cascode Current Mirror DAC
* Transistor-level implementation using SKY130 real devices
*
* Iout = Iunit x (8*b3 + 4*b2 + 2*b1 + b0)
* Range: code 1 (1x Iunit) to code 15 (15x Iunit)
* Nominal code = 8 (1000b)
*
* Reference side: diode-connected cascode pair driven by Iref
* Output side: binary-weighted cascode mirrors with NMOS switches
*
* Mirror NMOS:  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u
* Cascode NMOS: sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u
* Switch NMOS:  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=1u L=0.15u
*
* Digital inputs: 1.8V = ON, 0V = OFF

.subckt bias_dac_real iref iout vdd vss b0 b1 b2 b3

* === Reference side: diode-connected cascode ===
* Iref flows into drain of top cascode, sets gate_c and gate_n
* Bottom: diode-connected mirror transistor
XMref_bot  gate_n gate_n vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
* Top: diode-connected cascode transistor
XMref_cas  iref   iref   gate_n vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
* Gate_c is driven by iref node (diode connection at cascode drain=gate)
* Separate gate_c bias: use iref voltage directly for cascode gates
* Actually: the cascode gate should be a separate node for better compliance
* Use a dedicated bias: cascode gate = iref drain voltage
* Route cascode gate bias from the reference drain
Rg_cas iref gate_c 1
* This 1-ohm resistor separates the current input from the gate_c bus

* === Bit 0: 1x unit cell ===
XM0_bot  mid0  gate_n vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM0_cas  sw0d  gate_c mid0 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM0_sw   iout  b0     sw0d vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=1u L=0.15u nf=1
Rbleed0  sw0d  vss 100G

* === Bit 1: 2x unit cells ===
XM1a_bot mid1a gate_n vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM1a_cas sw1a  gate_c mid1a vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM1a_sw  iout  b1     sw1a  vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=1u L=0.15u nf=1
Rbleed1a sw1a  vss 100G

XM1b_bot mid1b gate_n vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM1b_cas sw1b  gate_c mid1b vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM1b_sw  iout  b1     sw1b  vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=1u L=0.15u nf=1
Rbleed1b sw1b  vss 100G

* === Bit 2: 4x unit cells ===
XM2a_bot mid2a gate_n vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM2a_cas sw2a  gate_c mid2a vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1
XM2a_sw  iout  b2     sw2a  vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=1u L=0.15u nf=1
Rbleed2a sw2a  vss 100G

